!"],[5935,6092,"my reputation."],[6252,6296,"So,"],[6419,6509,"I want to know"],[6593,6693,"who won this game, huh?"],[7190,7243,"I did."],[7467,7574,"Scarlett Hawkins."]],"20":[[50,236,"Well, Miss Hawkins,"],[236,407,"I must apologize."],[407,563,"My men can be a little, uh..."],[587,687,"what's the word..."],[687,807,"uncivilized."],[827,997,"I hope you don't take any offense."],[1131,1201,"No problem."],[1317,1478,"I'll just take what's mine and leave."],[1558,1718,"Actually, there is one thing."],[1748,1811,"Yeah?"],[1881,1945,"What is that?"],[2018,2208,"According to the rules of the casino,"],[2285,2435,"you have to cut off their hands."],[2445,2549,"- What? - No, please don't!"],[2549,2622,"That's right!"],[2639,2712,"It's the rules!"],[2712,2822,"Yeah, they cheated!"],[2822,2946,"Cut their hands off!"],[2946,3043,"- Cut their hands off! - Hands off!"],[3043,3253,"- Hands off! - Cut their hands off!"],[3259,3350,"Silence!"],[3620,3693,"Boss, please!"],[3727,3777,"You know me!"],[3777,3933,"You know I'd never do this to you, right?"],[3933,4124,"No, no, no, please!"],[4160,4284,"Please, please don't do it!"],[4290,4347,"No..."],[4477,4547,"Bring out the knife."],[4547,4611,"No!"],[4964,5025,"Actually,"],[5105,5268,"you don't have to cut off their hands."],[5308,5425,"I already taught them a lesson."],[5462,5538,"Besides,"],[5618,5705,"I'm afraid of blood."],[5979,6039,"Miss Scarlett,"],[6106,6166,"you..."],[6202,6322,"are quite generous."],[6740,6793,"You two..."],[6873,7040,"are lucky fucks."],[7197,7270,"Apologize."],[7323,7357,"I..."],[7530,7637,"I'm sorry, Ms. Scarlett."],[7637,7771,"I... I apologize."],[7881,7934,"I'm sorry."],[8038,8161,"Thank you for letting us keep our hands."],[8381,8481,"Guess it's my lucky day."],[8665,8745,"I appreciate it."],[8812,8888,"Thanks, everyone."],[9769,9999,"The real game has just begun."]],"21":[[40,93,"What?"],[110,213,"You're going back to..."],[353,457,"You're gonna wake Mia."],[633,790,"You're going back to gamble?"